The jar of swamp is a rare drop from Zulrah. Players who attempt to open it, will have the chatbox display the message I'm not opening that, it smells funny!

The jar can be used on a boss lair display in a player's Achievement Gallery to have a display of Zulrah. Doing so requires having defeated Zulrah at least once.
